Class AudienceRestrictionImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.saml2.assertion.impl.ConditionAbstractImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AudienceRestriction, ConditionAbstract

    public class AudienceRestrictionImpl
extends ConditionAbstractImpl
implements AudienceRestriction
    The AudienceRestriction specifies that the assertion is addressed to one or more specific Audiences.
